> I will not judge my strategy after one trade.
>
> I will not change my rules after one loss.
>
> I will not become overconfident after one win.
>
> I will trust data more than emotions.
>
> I will execute this playbook consistently for 100 trades.
>
> My goal is not to predict the market.
>
> My goal is to execute my edge with discipline.

---

## ✨ Core Philosophy

> ### One Instrument. One Primary Setup (S1). One Journal. One Playbook.
> ### Let statistics — not emotions — decide what changes after 100 trades.
